{
  "id": "69c708208d18d9f65803b21e",
  "title": "2026/03/28 Mijjiko",
  "created": 1774651424,
  "updated": 1774700686,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c708208d18d9f65803b21e",
      "text": "2026/03/28 Mijjiko",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774696170
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7b7ef00000000009851a9",
      "text": "[2026/03/28 Mijjiko infobox検証]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774696431,
      "updated": 1774696431
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7b7f000000000009851aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774696432,
      "updated": 1774696432
    },
    {
      "id": "69c797720000000000cf0a70",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688114,
      "updated": 1774688114
    },
    {
      "id": "69c797720000000000cf0a71",
      "text": "\tWindowsが起動の度に[BitLocker回復キー]求めるようになってマジだるい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688114,
      "updated": 1774688142
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7978f0000000000cf0a72",
      "text": "\t\tんでUEFIの設定吹っ飛んでたから戻そうとしたら今度はWindows自身（回復画面含め全て）起動しなくなるし",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688142,
      "updated": 1774688177
    },
    {
      "id": "69c797b30000000000cf0a73",
      "text": "\t\t[Windows Boot Manager]壊れてる？",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688178,
      "updated": 1774688189
    },
    {
      "id": "69c797be0000000000cf0a74",
      "text": "\t\tとりあえず[DISM.exe]と[sfc /scannow]かける",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688190,
      "updated": 1774688229
    },
    {
      "id": "69c797e60000000000cf0a75",
      "text": "\t\t\tこの手に限る",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688230,
      "updated": 1774688253
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7aa480000000000e4375a",
      "text": "\t\t\t・・・が今回は関係なかった",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774692936,
      "updated": 1774692941
    },
    {
      "id": "69c798580000000000cf0a76",
      "text": "\t\t後で[スタートアップ修復]も試してみる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688344,
      "updated": 1774688352
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7aa4e0000000000e4375b",
      "text": "\t\t\tエラーで動作しなかった",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774692942,
      "updated": 1774692957
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7ac920000000000e4376f",
      "text": "\t\t\t[Windows Boot Manager]を修復してみる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693521,
      "updated": 1774693541
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7acc40000000000e43773",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[bootrec.exe]が動かなかったので[bcdboot.exe]で修復した",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693572,
      "updated": 1774693593
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7acac0000000000e43771",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t$ bcdboot C:\\Windows /l ja-jp",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693548,
      "updated": 1774693552
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7acb00000000000e43772",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tドライブは[diskpart] > [list volume]で確認する",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693552,
      "updated": 1774693570
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7aca50000000000e43770",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[bootrec /RebuildBcd 指定されたパスがみつかりません #Windows10 - Qiita https://qiita.com/u-sho/items/39833d5a1e07a59410c0#%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E7%AD%96]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693541,
      "updated": 1774693546
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7acdd0000000000e43774",
      "text": "\t\t\t[Windows Boot Manager]を修復したら回復環境（[Windows RE]）がおかしくなった",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693597,
      "updated": 1774693677
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7acfe0000000000e43775",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[スタートアップ修復]等のメンテナンス項目が表示されない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693630,
      "updated": 1774693651
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7ad140000000000e43776",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこれは[ReAgentc.exe]を使えば元に戻った",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693651,
      "updated": 1774693849
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7ad460000000000e43777",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t$ reagentc /enable",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693702,
      "updated": 1774693703
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7ad480000000000e43778",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t$ reagentc /info",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693704,
      "updated": 1774693710
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7ad500000000000e43779",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t[Windows Server: 回復パーティション(WinRE)領域の移動および再構成の方法 | Dell 日本 https://www.dell.com/support/kbdoc/ja-jp/000222496/windows-server-%E5%9B%9E%E5%BE%A9%E3%83%91%E3%83%BC%E3%83%86%E3%82%A3%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%B3-winre-%E9%A0%98%E5%9F%9F%E3%81%AE%E5%86%8D%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693712,
      "updated": 1774693716
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7ad5a0000000000e4377a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t修復するだけだったら回復パーティションの作り直し手順は不要",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693722,
      "updated": 1774693748
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7aa5e0000000000e4375c",
      "text": "\t\t結局[TPM]が無効になっていたのが原因だった",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774692957,
      "updated": 1774692971
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7aad90000000000e43760",
      "text": "\t\t\t[PC起動時に毎回BitLockerの回復キーを求められる問題をどうにかする]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693081,
      "updated": 1774693110
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7aa6b0000000000e4375d",
      "text": "\t\t他に[Secure boot]を有効化するとWindowsが起動しなく鳴る問題もあった",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774692971,
      "updated": 1774693013
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7aa7f0000000000e4375e",
      "text": "\t\t\tこれは単純にセキュリティキーの復元方法を間違えていたのが原因",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774692991,
      "updated": 1774693060
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7aac50000000000e4375f",
      "text": "\t\t\tRestore from DBみたいな項目で復元しないとダメだった",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774693061,
      "updated": 1774693073
    },
    {
      "id": "69c797720000000000cf0a6f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688114,
      "updated": 1774688114
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c87000000000009a3f85",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774700656,
      "updated": 1774700656
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c87100000000009a3f87",
      "text": "\tマイクもう少し検討するか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774700656,
      "updated": 1774700666
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c87a00000000009a3f88",
      "text": "\t[2026/03/22 みじっこマイク]で続き書く",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774700666,
      "updated": 1774700686
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7c87000000000009a3f86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774700656,
      "updated": 1774700656
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708390000000000cd2f93",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon] from [2026/03/28] ([2026-03-28])",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651449,
      "updated": 1774696188
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f7c",
      "text": " [嫌いなもの多い人]、そもそも不特定多数のコミュニティあんま向いてないと思う",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f7d",
      "text": " 　嫌いなもの少ないとこ見つけられたらラッキーだけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f7e",
      "text": " 　そうじゃなきゃ自分がいる場所で妥協して声を大きくするしかないね",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f7f",
      "text": " [自分の中と外の境界が曖昧な人]も、苦労するだろうな",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f80",
      "text": " 　自分に全く関係の無いことなのに自分が虐げられていると錯覚するようなね",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f81",
      "text": " 　全く関係ない訳ないって？",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f82",
      "text": " 　　いや、どう考えても全く関係ないよ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f83",
      "text": " 　その人がかわいそう←そうだね",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f84",
      "text": " 　虐げた人は許せない←そうだね",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f85",
      "text": " 　悲しくなってきた←そうだね",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f86",
      "text": " 　自分だって虐げられた人と同じだ←それは違う",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f87",
      "text": " 　共感するなと言いたい訳じゃないけど、共感すると苦しむことになるから（やめれるなら）やめた方がいいとは思う",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f88",
      "text": " [心の余裕]って健康と睡眠からしか得られない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f89",
      "text": " 　人のこと馬鹿にしまくっているけどそんなはずじゃないんだ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f8a",
      "text": " 　もっと寝たいし休みたい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f8b",
      "text": " 　この世の大抵のものは愚かだが",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f8c",
      "text": " 　　その愚かさを切り捨てずに活路を見出した人がいるから発明ができるのだ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f8d",
      "text": " 　　発明者になりたいな",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f8e",
      "text": " 　ああ、最も知ってる愚かな人間は自分だ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f8f",
      "text": " 　　どう使えばいい？ハウトゥユーズ？",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f90",
      "text": " 　　モノの価値は相対的だ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f91",
      "text": " 　　自分の価値が自分でわかる筈もない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651461
    },
    {
      "id": "69c708210000000000cd2f92",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651424,
      "updated": 1774651424
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7088d00000000004bed2c",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651532,
      "updated": 1774651534
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7088e00000000004bed2e",
      "text": " ねむいねんな",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651534,
      "updated": 1774651538
    },
    {
      "id": "69c70e230000000000af3d81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774652963,
      "updated": 1774652963
    },
    {
      "id": "69c70e230000000000af3d82",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774652963,
      "updated": 1774652964
    },
    {
      "id": "69c70e250000000000af3d83",
      "text": "　背中パキパキ鳴るよたすけてー",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774652965,
      "updated": 1774652980
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7088d00000000004bed2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774651532,
      "updated": 1774688111
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7976b0000000000cf0a6c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774688107,
      "updated": 1774688107
    }
  ]
}